{"tid":113463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(無正體漢字)來台旅客創新高 蔡英文推特9種語言道謝","createTime":"2017-02-09T03:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T04:04:38.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c66d0aff49dde204360b6ced18a3da7ccffbe5d","tid":113463,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T03:51:11.000Z","msg":"來台旅客創新高 蔡英文推特9種語言道謝<br />\n<br />\n政治中心／綜合報導&nbsp;<br />\n2017-02-09 09:31<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.peoplenews.tw/news/16ed9ac7-4f7f-434c-8e03-7fe4f3dc2659.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.peoplenews.tw%2Fnews%2F16ed9ac7-4f7f-434c-8e03-7fe4f3dc2659.jpg&h=8eb00bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡英文總統在推特上以9種語言向來台觀光客道謝。（圖片擷取自蔡英文臉書）<br />\n<br />\n行政院主計總處日前發佈國情統計通報顯示，2016年來台旅客達1069萬人次，創下歷史新高。總統蔡英文今天特別在推特用9種語言，表達感謝；其中，「謝謝」兩字用的是簡體中文，而9種語言中就有五種語言為東南亞與南亞國家，向東南亞地區來台旅客致意。<br />\n<br />\n主計總處日前發布國情統計通報指出，105年來台旅客達1069萬人次，為歷史新高，較104年成長2.4%。其中，觀光簽證簡化措施帶動東南亞旅客大幅成長，泰國旅客來台人次大增5成7。<br />\n<br />\n對於來台觀光人數創新高，蔡總統今早在推特發文，特別用了多種語言，表達感謝。蔡總統分別用了，英文、中國字（簡字）、日文、韓文、泰文、印尼文、菲律賓語、越南文、印度文。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.peoplenews.tw/news/16ed9ac7-4f7f-434c-8e03-7fe4f3dc2659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.peoplenews.tw%2Fnews%2F16ed9ac7-4f7f-434c-8e03-7fe4f3dc2659&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=5ab77b6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.peoplenews.tw/news/16ed9ac7-4f7f-434c-8e03-7fe4f3dc2659</a>"},{"pid":"1afe4e61f98346bab5dadca72eb66c7821e1022f","tid":113463,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T03:52:03.000Z","msg":"港澳係用正體字"},{"pid":"7f1d87c5e2c1284c60c49eed3415577a48170a8b","tid":113463,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a35c4d7746bde4b8e0dbb32e19814b336265d76","tid":113463,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"佢地自己都用洗乜推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac2310fe32a4a257e91237c3ee39170e3c4e51f","tid":113463,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"應該用埋繁體字：多謝"},{"pid":"96901da81800aceb460e38210c2a09788dc2cd64","tid":113463,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:04:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港澳係用正體字</blockquote><br />\n咪淨係得港澳囉，咁佢打嘅字淨係畀旅客睇，但港澳客佔咁少，唔出好正常"},{"pid":"fbedd1bef7689766b113bd7fc1c7e06fc5f605a9","tid":113463,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T04:04:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地自己都用洗乜推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 原來推特"}]}